name: Marina Kriofske
text: Pizza and wings are great but they always forget our marinara sauce 99% of the time getting super annoying .

name: Phil Traz
text: Tried to order the "Order 2 or more for $5" as per the ad IN THE STORE. Told that it was not valid and would not be accepted. Had to get a manager involved for them to accept the ad that was posted at the register. …More

name: jim campbell
text: Wings and a meat lover deep dish pizza at home or in the car can't beat it ! plates and wipes provided ,  with just one call you get it all !

name: High Speed
text: Placed a very large order the day before, came in to pick it up and everything was ready on time and the order was correct. The manager Megan was very helpful and accommodating. Food was delicious!

name: Stephanie Lubinski
text: Food delivered super fast and piping hot! Stuffed crust pizza was cook perfectly crust was crispy and inside soft.....delicious! The wing street bone in wings were better than I have had at most restaurants! Great job!

name: Don Heese
text: Pizza Hut is back Muskego!! And I dare say they have even improved a bit. Currently it appears they offer dine in and carry out. I ordered carry out and it was ready in a speedy 15 minutes. It would be great if they eventually offer delivery. Happy to have them back.

name: Dave Friesner
text: Excellent service good price and quick

name: Sarah H
text: I miss the old pizza hut pizza! :(  Was so excited for stuffed crust and it was SO sad.  Super thin droopy crust and finding the cheese in the crust was a treasure hunt.

name: Rib
text: Terrible quality, tried the new pizza hut a few times and its just BAD! Just order Dominos or Papa Johns.

name: Matt Ameti
text: Brand new store open with a dining room and a great staff

name: Justin Buie
text: Happy to have a new Pizza Hut I’m muskego everyone go check them out!

name: Kerry
text: Pizza is always good and fast

name: Taryn Volbrecht
text: I made an error when placing my order online; but without hesitating the manager corrected MY error and I left the restaurant with my intended order at no extra cost.

name: Jacob Piotrowski
text: 9 minutes from my house and no delivery???
